title: JACOBS' DREAM: IMPROVING DISASTER RISK MANAGEMENT USING VISUAL CLUES IN

title: JACOBS' DREAM: IMPROVING DISASTER RISK MANAGEMENT USING VISUAL CLUES IN

title: JACOBS' DREAM: IMPROVING DISASTER RISK MANAGEMENT USING VISUAL CLUES IN

title: JACOBS' DREAM: IMPROVING DISASTER RISK MANAGEMENT USING VISUAL CLUES IN

title: JACOBS' DREAM: IMPROVING DISASTER RISK MANAGEMENT USING VISUAL CLUES IN

title: JACOBS' DREAM: IMPROVING DISASTER RISK MANAGEMENT USING VISUAL CLUES IN

sentence: To achieve the benefits AI offers and meet the rising global competition, America needs an AI Opportunity Agenda.
title: Joint Economic Committee Issues Testimony From R Street Institute Senior Fellow

sentence: An AI Opportunity Agenda begins by reiterating that the freedom to innovate is the cornerstone of American
title: Joint Economic Committee Issues Testimony From R Street Institute Senior Fellow

sentence: technology policy and the key to unlocking the enormous potential of our nation's entrepreneurs and workers.16 As
title: Joint Economic Committee Issues Testimony From R Street Institute Senior Fellow

sentence: part of this Agenda, Congress should craft a learning period moratorium on new proposals, such as new AI-specific
title: Joint Economic Committee Issues Testimony From R Street Institute Senior Fellow

sentence: bureaucracies, licensing systems, or liability schemes, all of which would be counterproductive and undermine our
title: Joint Economic Committee Issues Testimony From R Street Institute Senior Fellow

sentence: nation's computational capabilities. [See Enclosure I] In addition, this moratorium should preempt burdensome state
title: Joint Economic Committee Issues Testimony From R Street Institute Senior Fellow

sentence: and local regulatory enactments that conflict with our national AI policy framework.17
title: Joint Economic Committee Issues Testimony From R Street Institute Senior Fellow

sentence: Next, Congress should require our government's existing 439 federal departments to evaluate their current policies
title: Joint Economic Committee Issues Testimony From R Street Institute Senior Fellow

sentence: toward AI systems with two purposes in mind. First, to ensure that they are not over-burdening algorithmic systems
title: Joint Economic Committee Issues Testimony From R Street Institute Senior Fellow

sentence: with outdated policies, and second, to determine how existing rules and regulations are capable of addressing the
title: Joint Economic Committee Issues Testimony From R Street Institute Senior Fellow

sentence: concerns that some have raised about AI. Taking inventory of existing rules and regulations can then allow
title: Joint Economic Committee Issues Testimony From R Street Institute Senior Fellow

sentence: policymakers to identify any gaps that Congress ought to address using targeted remedies.
title: Joint Economic Committee Issues Testimony From R Street Institute Senior Fellow

sentence: Finally, an AI Opportunity Agenda requires an openness to new talent and competition.18 With experts finding that
title: Joint Economic Committee Issues Testimony From R Street Institute Senior Fellow

sentence: a "talent war is brewing between the US and China," and that China is moving ahead in some important ways, we
title: Joint Economic Committee Issues Testimony From R Street Institute Senior Fellow

sentence: must take steps to attract and retain the world's best and brightest data scientists and computer engineers.19

title: DEPARTMENT OF HOMELAND SECURITY UNVEILS ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE

title: DEPARTMENT OF HOMELAND SECURITY UNVEILS ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE

title: DEPARTMENT OF HOMELAND SECURITY UNVEILS ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE

title: DEPARTMENT OF HOMELAND SECURITY UNVEILS ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE

title: DEPARTMENT OF HOMELAND SECURITY UNVEILS ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE

sentence: A doctoral candidate at The University of Alabama in Huntsville (UAH) is lead author of a new study in the
title: UAH Researcher Publishes Study Tapping Social Media and AI to Speed Supply Chain

sentence: International Journal of Production Research investigating the ways social media platforms can be leveraged with
title: UAH Researcher Publishes Study Tapping Social Media and AI to Speed Supply Chain

title: UAH Researcher Publishes Study Tapping Social Media and AI to Speed Supply Chain

title: UAH Researcher Publishes Study Tapping Social Media and AI to Speed Supply Chain

title: UAH Researcher Publishes Study Tapping Social Media and AI to Speed Supply Chain

sentence: Sampson Gholston, as well as Kumar's mentor, Dr. Siva K. Balasubramanian of the Illinois Institute of Technology,
title: UAH Researcher Publishes Study Tapping Social Media and AI to Speed Supply Chain

sentence: to support the initiative.
title: UAH Researcher Publishes Study Tapping Social Media and AI to Speed Supply Chain

sentence: For the project, the team used data from X, formerly known as Twitter, from two six-week time periods and two
title: UAH Researcher Publishes Study Tapping Social Media and AI to Speed Supply Chain

sentence: countries during the COVID-19 pandemic: March-April 2020 in the United States when the pandemic broke out, and
title: UAH Researcher Publishes Study Tapping Social Media and AI to Speed Supply Chain

sentence: in India during the surge of the delta variant in May-June 2021. Disruptions in health care supply chains during
title: UAH Researcher Publishes Study Tapping Social Media and AI to Speed Supply Chain

sentence: these periods were causing severe shortages of essential equipment ranging from face masks and medicines to
title: UAH Researcher Publishes Study Tapping Social Media and AI to Speed Supply Chain

sentence: ventilators for patients in intensive care.
title: UAH Researcher Publishes Study Tapping Social Media and AI to Speed Supply Chain

sentence: "I was born and raised in the countryside of India, in Sitamarhi, Bihar, near the Nepal border, where natural
title: UAH Researcher Publishes Study Tapping Social Media and AI to Speed Supply Chain

sentence: disasters such as floods from the Himalayan rivers are frequent," Kumar says to explain the initial spark driving his
title: UAH Researcher Publishes Study Tapping Social Media and AI to Speed Supply Chain

sentence: vision to help. "These floods can spread over miles, trapping thousands of people in their homes who need urgent
title: UAH Researcher Publishes Study Tapping Social Media and AI to Speed Supply Chain

sentence: help for healthcare and food, as well as rescue operations. From a young age, I was driven to develop a framework
title: UAH Researcher Publishes Study Tapping Social Media and AI to Speed Supply Chain

sentence: that would enable people in need to communicate their requirements to the world and relevant authorities so they
title: UAH Researcher Publishes Study Tapping Social Media and AI to Speed Supply Chain

sentence: coordinate to assist disaster victims on time."
title: UAH Researcher Publishes Study Tapping Social Media and AI to Speed Supply Chain

sentence: The COVID-19 pandemic in 2020 presented a disaster of a different kind, affecting billions of people worldwide and
title: UAH Researcher Publishes Study Tapping Social Media and AI to Speed Supply Chain

sentence: exposing significant vulnerabilities in global healthcare supply chains. Critical shortages of essential supplies like
title: UAH Researcher Publishes Study Tapping Social Media and AI to Speed Supply Chain

title: UAH Researcher Publishes Study Tapping Social Media and AI to Speed Supply Chain

title: UAH Researcher Publishes Study Tapping Social Media and AI to Speed Supply Chain

title: UAH Researcher Publishes Study Tapping Social Media and AI to Speed Supply Chain

title: UAH Researcher Publishes Study Tapping Social Media and AI to Speed Supply Chain

title: UAH Researcher Publishes Study Tapping Social Media and AI to Speed Supply Chain
